name: ACRE DAOs Angels
description: Sponsorship Pool for ACRE DAOs Web3 Impact Investment Club, a diverse community of change agents who believe that large numbers of people can effectively and dynamically organize for the funding of targeted regenerative solutions.
payDisclosure: Your gift supports our mission to keep ACRE DAOs community membership accessible to all, and ensures that the meaningful engagement of passionate people in Autonomous Communities for Regenerative Economies (ACRE) is financially sustainable without regard to their income level or amount of investible assets.
